  <summary date="2019-07-06T14:02:05Z" status="Introduced in House">Ending One-Ring Scams Act of 2019

This bill requires the Federal Communications Commission to initiate a proceeding to protect called parties from one-ring scams. These scams generally involve illegal robocallers hanging up after one ring, with the goal of having the targeted person call them back.</summary>
